dialogue: I can't believe I'm alone out here.
description: A lone astronaut floats in the vastness of space, surrounded by darkness and silence.

dialogue: My communication system is down. No one can hear me.
description: The astronaut frantically tries to repair their equipment, but to no avail. They are completely cut off from the outside world.

dialogue: I don't know how long I can survive out here without any help.
description: The astronaut's heart races as they realize the gravity of their situation. They must find a way to stay alive until they can be rescued.
